views.markdown:
- Added iOS 13 support - Fixed not being able to dismiss or open an application from bulletins in iOS 10
- Fixed bulletin soundID issue on iOS 10
- Fixed crash on iOS10 when unlocking by sliding a bulletin - Fixes NULL bundleID crash - Fixed an iOS 10 issue that prevented bulletins from being dismissed at lockscreen - Added iOS 10 support - Added -updateBulletin and -removeBulletin methods for real-time management of lockscreen bulletins.
